{"tid":519652,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【黑警醜聞】33歲休班黑警涉旺角站偷拍16歲少女裙底   下周四提堂","createTime":"2018-01-04T14:45:06.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-04T16:07:52.000Z","uid":79563,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"ea1fae569fa793a9e2936e908304a4ae637aa890","tid":519652,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-04T14:45:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180104/large/1515073617_bb90.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180104%2Flarge%2F1515073617_bb90.jpg&h=c5ca857d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n黑警連環爆出醜聞，33歲休班男黑警涉嫌於去年1月21日下午在港鐵旺角站乘搭扶手電梯時，用手機偷拍16歲少女的裙底。黑警經進一步調查及徵詢法律意見後，昨日拘捕該名警員，落案控以一項破壞公眾體統罪，案件將於下周四(11日)在西九龍裁判法院提堂。<br />\n<br />\n黑警表示，黑警非常重視人員的操守，任何人員干犯違法行為，警隊絕不容忍和姑息，定必嚴正處理，進行刑事調查及紀律覆檢。"},{"pid":"aac9d59307b0f54520c5e615f572131604a9ca4f","tid":519652,"uid":61280,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-04T14:47:44.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">大驚小怪！！！&lt;img src=&quot;/assets/faces/xm/ass.gif&quot; class=&quot;hkgmoji pixelated&quot; /&gt; <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n阿犬攪野，唔洗你教！！！！</span></span></strong><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/01/04/223314_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F01%2F04%2F223314_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png&h=f2544223&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/01/04/224741_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F01%2F04%2F224741_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png&h=55557592&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"470325ed331be85b2b3dc46bc2a7926a3d05df65","tid":519652,"uid":61280,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-04T15:05:22.000Z","msg":